column8: Those three guys that plunge into the pool, naked, hidden, like a wind in the life of Teresa. Are little more than children, their bodies and uncontrolled desires and pure, just like her. The next 20 years will pass them together in the farmhouse next door, to sow, reap, destroy, the mad search for a fire keep them lit. At the center of everything there is always Bern, a magnet that attracts others and pushes them over the edge, with the intensity of someone who knows only absolute passions: God, sex, nature, a son.
